"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=us+national+news+site:foxnews.com","Fitness expert visits gyms nationwide, shouts out 4 clubs for 'getting it right'","https://www.foxnews.com/health/fitness-expert-visits-gyms-nationwide-shouts-4-clubs-getting-right","Sat, 09 May 2026 13:00:57 GMT","


