"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:pagesix.com","‘Vanderpump Rules' alums Tom Sandoval, Ariana Madix quietly sell former love nest after messy split","https://pagesix.com/2026/05/08/lifestyle/vanderpump-rules-alums-tom-sandoval-ariana-madix-sell-shared-house-after-messy-split/","Sat, 09 May 2026 01:17:00 GMT","

Ariana Madix and Tom Sandoval quietly sold their formerly shared LA home three years after their messy breakup. 

Sources claim the couple was able to sell the Valley Village farmhouse for $3.1 million on Friday, reports TMZ. 

Page Six previously posted an inside look at the Broadway star and Sandoval's former residence, which features a large contemporary kitchen with beautiful white marble countertops, light wood flooring, a spacious living room and den with a view of the backyard, and ritzy light fixtures.

Advertisement

The primary bedroom holds enough space to fit a king-sized bed, extra seating and a sizable dresser.

Advertisement

The exes decorated the room with mirrors, wood ottomans, low-sitting side tables and a green velour bedframe.

Madix and Sandoval purchased the sprawling abode in 2019 — five years into their relationship — for $2 million. 

